          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Take advantage of Cyberweek savings across our entire range of premium products. Explore top-quality designs from industry-leading brands, all at discounted prices:</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/kitchen-tapware\" title=\"Kitchen Tapware & Mixers\"><strong>Kitchen Tapware</strong></a>:</p><p>Upgrade your kitchen with premium tapware from <a href=\"/collections/franke-tapware\" title=\"Franke Tapware\"><strong>Franke</strong></a>, <a href=\"/collections/kitchen-tapware-by-phoenix\" title=\"Kitchen Tapware by Phoenix\"><strong>Phoenix Tapware</strong></a>, and <a href=\"/collections/villeroy-boch-kitchen-tapware\" title=\"Villeroy & Boch Kitchen Tapware\"><strong>Villeroy & Boch</strong></a>. Choose from sleek gooseneck mixers, pull-out taps, and modern designs that blend functionality with style. Perfect for a contemporary or classic kitchen makeover.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/basins-and-sinks\" title=\"Basins and Sinks\"><strong>Sinks & Basins</strong></a>:</p><p>Discover a wide variety of sinks and basins on sale from trusted names like <strong>Franke</strong>, <a href=\"/collections/bourne\" title=\"Bourne\"><strong>Bourne</strong></a>, and <strong>Villeroy & Boch</strong>. Whether you’re after a classic stainless-steel sink or a modern ceramic basin, our range has something for every home.</p><p>\t•\t<strong>Bathroom Accessories</strong>:</p><p>Add the finishing touches to your bathroom with accessories from <a href=\"/collections/phoenix-bathroom-accessories\" title=\"Phoenix Bathroom Accessories\"><strong>Phoenix Tapware</strong></a>, <a href=\"/collections/fienza\" title=\"Fienza\"><strong>Fienza</strong></a>, and <a href=\"/collections/otti\" title=\"Otti\"><strong>Otti</strong></a>. From towel rails and soap dishes to stylish shower niches, these essentials will elevate the look and feel of your space.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/laundry\" title=\"Laundry\"><strong>Laundry Products</strong></a>:</p><p>Refresh your laundry with top-tier sinks, tapware, and accessories from brands like <strong>Franke</strong>, <strong>Bourne</strong>, and <strong>Timberline</strong>. With innovative designs and durable materials, these products are built to last.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/showers\" title=\"Showers\"><strong>Showers</strong></a>:</p><p>Upgrade your bathroom with premium shower options from <strong>Phoenix Tapware</strong>, <strong>Fienza</strong>, and <a href=\"/collections/caroma\" title=\"Caroma\"><strong>Caroma</strong></a>. Explore rain showers, handheld options, and sleek wall-mounted designs that combine functionality with luxury. Perfect for creating a relaxing, spa-like experience at home.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/shower-bases\" title=\"Shower Bases\"><strong>Shower Bases & Shower Floors</strong>:</a></p><p>Complete your shower setup with durable shower bases and stylish shower floors from <a href=\"/collections/domus-living\" title=\"Domus Living\"><strong>Domus Living,</strong></a> <a href=\"/collections/marbletrend\" title=\"Marbletrend Shower Bases\"><strong>Marbletrend</strong></a>. Crafted for long-lasting performance, these products ensure a seamless and watertight foundation for any shower design.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/baths\" title=\"Baths\"><strong>Baths</strong></a>:</p><p>Indulge in elegance with freestanding and built-in baths from <strong>Phoenix Tapware</strong>, <strong>Fienza</strong>, and <strong>Caroma</strong>. Designed for ultimate comfort and style, these baths are the perfect centrepiece for any bathroom.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/vanity-units\" title=\"Vanities\"><strong>Vanities</strong></a>:</p><p>Elevate your bathroom with stunning vanities from <strong>Timberline</strong>, <strong>Fienza</strong>, and <strong>Bourne</strong>. Choose from compact single vanities to luxurious double vanities, all featuring soft-close drawers and premium finishes like solid surface tops. Perfect for any bathroom style or size.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/ovens\" title=\"Ovens\"><strong>Ovens</strong></a>:</p><p>Experience precision cooking with our range of ovens from <strong>Smeg</strong>, <strong>Electrolux</strong>, and <strong>Euro Appliances</strong>. Choose from multifunction ovens, pyrolytic self-cleaning options, and compact models designed for efficiency and style. Perfect for both home cooks and gourmet chefs.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/cooktops\" title=\"Cooktops\"><strong>Cooktops</strong></a>:</p><p>Take control of your cooking with high-quality cooktops, including induction, gas, and ceramic options. Brands like <strong>Smeg</strong>, <strong>Euro Appliances</strong>, and <strong>Electrolux</strong> offer sleek designs and advanced technology for every type of kitchen.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/rangehoods\" title=\"Rangehoods\"><strong>Rangehoods</strong></a>:</p><p>Keep your kitchen fresh and odour-free with rangehoods from <strong>Smeg</strong>, <strong>Euro Appliances</strong>, and <strong>Electrolux</strong>. Explore undermount, canopy, and wall-mounted designs that combine powerful performance with modern aesthetics.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/dishwashers\" title=\"Dishwashers\"><strong>Dishwashers</strong></a>:</p><p>Simplify your cleaning routine with energy-efficient dishwashers from <strong>Smeg</strong>, <strong>Euro Appliances</strong>, and <strong>Electrolux</strong>. With spacious designs, quiet operation, and water-saving technology, these dishwashers are built to handle even the busiest kitchens.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/microwaves\" title=\"Microwaves\"><strong>Microwaves</strong></a>:</p><p>Find versatile microwaves from <strong>Smeg</strong>, <strong>Euro Appliances</strong>, and <strong>Electrolux</strong> that offer quick heating, defrosting, and advanced cooking features. Perfect for busy households needing fast and reliable solutions.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/freestanding-ovens\" title=\"Freestanding Ovens\"><strong>Freestanding Ovens</strong></a><strong>:</strong></p><p>Combine oven and cooktop functionality with stylish freestanding cookers from <strong>Smeg</strong> and <strong>Euro Appliances</strong>. Available in various sizes and finishes, these cookers deliver convenience and elegance in one appliance.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/fridges-kitchen\" title=\"Fridges\"><strong>Fridges</strong></a>:</p><p>Preserve your food in style with modern fridges and freezers from <strong>Electrolux</strong> and <strong>Euro Appliances</strong>. From sleek French-door designs to compact upright freezers, find options that meet your storage needs and energy efficiency goals.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/tapware-bathroom\" title=\"Bathroom Tapware\"><strong>Bathroom Tapware</strong></a>:</p><p>Upgrade your bathroom with stylish tapware from <strong>Phoenix Tapware</strong>, <strong>Fienza</strong>, and <strong>Caroma</strong>. Explore elegant basin mixers, wall-mounted taps, and freestanding bath spouts, all crafted for durability and timeless design.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/mirrors\" title=\"Mirrors\"><strong>Mirrors</strong></a>:</p><p>Add functionality and style to your space with mirrors from <strong>Otti</strong> and <strong>Timberline</strong>. Choose from LED-lit designs, copper-free options, or classic frameless styles to suit any decor. Perfect for adding light and depth to your bathroom or dressing area.</p><p>\t•\t<a href=\"/collections/toilets\" title=\"Modern Toilets & Cisterns\"><strong>Toilets</strong></a>:</p><p>Discover premium toilets from <strong>Villeroy & Boch</strong>, <strong>Fienza</strong>, and <strong>Caroma</strong> at Cyberweek prices. From compact wall-faced designs to rimless technology for effortless cleaning, these toilets combine comfort and style for every bathroom.</p><p>\t•\t<strong>Accessories & Finishing Touches</strong>:</p><p>Complete your renovation with discounted accessories from <strong>Phoenix Tapware</strong>, <strong>Franke</strong>, and <strong>Timberline</strong>. Explore soap dispensers, kitchen racks, and bathroom organizers designed to enhance functionality and aesthetic appeal.</p><p><br/></p><p>With exclusive discounts on these collections and more, there’s no better time to shop at Cook & Bathe.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
