    "rich_text_3FidG9": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_VrPgyz": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p><strong>Shop Online or Visit Our Showroom</strong></p>",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_b9Ffxh": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Enjoy a seamless shopping experience tailored to your needs. Browse our extensive collections online from the comfort of your home, or visit our showroom to explore the products in person. Our knowledgeable consultants are ready to assist you in finding the perfect solutions for your kitchen, bathroom, or laundry. Whether you’re undertaking a complete renovation or simply refreshing a space, <strong>Cook & Bathe’s Cyberweek Sale</strong> has everything you need to bring your vision to life.</p><p>We also offer a reliable <strong>national delivery service</strong>, ensuring your purchases arrive promptly and safely, no matter where you are in Australia.</p><p>For personalised advice or to see our products up close, visit our showroom or <a href=\"/pages/contact\" title=\"Contact\"><strong>contact us here</strong> </a>to speak with our friendly team.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_VrPgyz",
        "text_b9Ffxh"
      ],
